data.description: Proudly presenting 165 Arrowhead Circle, Newfoundland, PA, a classic single family Sprawling Ranch style home built in 2007. This inviting home sprawls over a generous .92-acre plot and offers over 3000 sq. ft. of living space. This well-designed home boasts 4 spacious bedrooms with primary suite featuring an attached ensuite bathroom.  The freshly painted interior design highlights include gleaming hardwood flooring and an open floor plan that flows seamlessly into the kitchen showcasing an attractive layout.  Plus, the home is warmed up by woods stoves, nurturing a cozy atmosphere. An additional basement area serves as a great functional space.  Externally, the home showcases a tastefully landscaped design on a low traffic street, huge yard for the kids to play.
